Source: rk3566-camera-dtbo
Maintainer: MYSh LLC <maksym.shevchenko@mysh.studio>
Section: misc
Priority: optional
Standards-Version: 4.6.0
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), device-tree-compiler

Package: rk3566-camera-dtbo
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: v4l-utils
Description: Device tree overlays for RK3566 cameras and HDMI-CSI bridges
 Provides device tree overlays for camera support on RK3566 SoC:
 .
  - IMX219 (Raspberry Pi Camera v2)
  - OV5647 (Raspberry Pi Camera v1.3)
  - IMX477 (Raspberry Pi HQ Camera)
  - GC2053 (Galaxy Core 2MP)
  - TC358743 (Toshiba HDMI to CSI-2 bridge)
 .
 Includes camera-overlay utility for easy enable/disable of camera overlays.
 TC358743 HDMI-CSI bridge includes automatic EDID setup via systemd service.
 Compatible with Radxa Zero 3W and similar RK3566-based boards.
